<LanguageData>
    
    <!-- EN: challenging acceptance -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.challenging_acceptance.label>有保留的接纳</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.challenging_acceptance.label>
    <!-- EN: I knew it wouldn't be easy for my lover to be accepted by everyone. Their wary glances cut deeper than I expected. -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.challenging_acceptance.description>我知道我的爱人要想被大家接受并不容易。他们警惕的目光比我想象的更深。</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.challenging_acceptance.description>
    <!-- EN: unwavering love -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.unwavering_love.label>坚定不移的爱</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.unwavering_love.label>
    <!-- EN: I knew it wouldn't be easy for my lover to be accepted by everyone. Their wary glances cut deeper than I expected. But our love will stand strong, even if it means facing the world alone together. -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.unwavering_love.description>我知道我的爱人要想被大家接受并不容易。他们警惕的目光比我想象的更深。但我们的爱将坚不可摧，即使这意味着我们要一起独自面对这个世界。</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.unwavering_love.description>
    <!-- EN: love triumphs -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.love_triumphs.label>爱的胜利</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.love_triumphs.label>
    <!-- EN: It's a gamble. But our love proves that even in the harshest corners of the galaxy, compassion can flourish. -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.love_triumphs.description>很难不说这是一场赌博，但我们的爱证明，即使在最严酷的角落，同情心也能盛开。</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.love_triumphs.description>
    <!-- EN: heartbreak's weight -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.heartbreaks_weight.label>心碎的分量</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.heartbreaks_weight.label>
    <!-- EN: The rejection stings more than I thought possible. I hoped for a shared future, a dream of unity and love, but now I'm left grappling with the pieces of a hope that feels shattered. -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.heartbreaks_weight.description>拒绝的刺痛超出了我的想象。我希望有一个共同的未来，一个团结友爱的梦想，但现在我却只能在希望的碎片中挣扎，感受希望破灭的痛苦。</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.heartbreaks_weight.description>
    <!-- EN: reluctant farewell -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.reluctant_farewell.label>再见</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.reluctant_farewell.label>
    <!-- EN: After much soul-searching, I've realized that our paths must part. It's a decision that burdens my heart with sorrow, like abandoning a part of myself. -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.reluctant_farewell.description>经过深思熟虑，我意识到我们的路必须分开。这个决定让我的内心充满悲伤，就像抛弃了自己的一部分。</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.reluctant_farewell.description>
    <!-- EN: hopeful release -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.hopeful_release.label>分手快乐</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.hopeful_release.label>
    <!-- EN: Though parting ways was painful, it's given us both the chance to find our own paths. It's the time for new beginnings. -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.hopeful_release.description>虽然分道扬镳是痛苦的，但这给了我们俩寻找自己道路的机会。现在是新的开始。</RotR_BoFLoverMood.stages.hopeful_release.description>
    
    <!-- EN: reject my lover's joining -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverOpinion.stages.reject_my_lovers_joining.label>拒绝我的恋人的加入</RotR_BoFLoverOpinion.stages.reject_my_lovers_joining.label>
    <!-- EN: accept my lover's joining -->
    <RotR_BoFLoverOpinion.stages.accept_my_lovers_joining.label>接受我的恋人的加入</RotR_BoFLoverOpinion.stages.accept_my_lovers_joining.label>
    
    <!-- EN: shadows of doubt -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.shadows_of_doubt.label>怀疑的阴云</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.shadows_of_doubt.label>
    <!-- EN: Even here, amidst my newfound freedom, I sense some eyes hold reservations, whispers of my past following me. -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.shadows_of_doubt.description>在这一刻，在我新获得的自由中，我也感觉到有些目光有所保留，我的过去在低声追随着我。</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.shadows_of_doubt.description>
    <!-- EN: unwavering love -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.unwavering_love.label>坚定不移的爱</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.unwavering_love.label>
    <!-- EN: Even here, amidst my newfound freedom, I sense some eyes hold reservations, whispers of my past following me. But our love will stand strong, even if it means facing the world alone together. -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.unwavering_love.description>在这一刻，在我新获得的自由中，我也感觉到有些目光有所保留，我的过去在我身后悄悄流淌。但我们的爱将坚不可摧，哪怕这意味着我们要一起独自面对这个世界。</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.unwavering_love.description>
    <!-- EN: embraced by love -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.embraced_by_love.label>被爱所拥</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.embraced_by_love.label>
    <!-- EN: To be accepted and loved in this new home, despite where I come from, fills me with hope. -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.embraced_by_love.description>不管我来自何方，但在这个新家园里被接纳、被关爱，让我充满希望。</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.embraced_by_love.description>
    <!-- EN: burden of refusal -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.burden_of_refusal.label>拒绝之重</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.burden_of_refusal.label>
    <!-- EN: The weight of what could have been—a life of love and acceptance—now haunts me, leaving a void filled with regret and what-ifs. -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.burden_of_refusal.description>本可以拥有的一切--充满爱和被接纳的生活--萦绕在我的心头，留下了充满遗憾和 "如果 "的空白。</RotR_BoFSlaveMood.stages.burden_of_refusal.description>
    
    <!-- EN: reject my joining -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveOpinion.stages.reject_my_joining.label>拒绝了我的加入</RotR_BoFSlaveOpinion.stages.reject_my_joining.label>
    <!-- EN: accept my joining -->
    <RotR_BoFSlaveOpinion.stages.accept_my_joining.label>欢迎我的加入</RotR_BoFSlaveOpinion.stages.accept_my_joining.label>
    
    <!-- EN: tensions over newcomer -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.tensions_over_newcomer.label>新人带来的紧张</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.tensions_over_newcomer.label>
    <!-- EN: I just hope that former slave won't disrupt the harmony of our colony. -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.tensions_over_newcomer.description>我只希望那个前奴隶不要破坏我们殖民地的和谐。</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.tensions_over_newcomer.description>
    <!-- EN: new bonds of unity -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.new_bonds_of_unity.label>连结的纽带</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.new_bonds_of_unity.label>
    <!-- EN: Seeing newcomer find freedom and love among us really warms my heart. -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.new_bonds_of_unity.description>看到新人在我们中间找到自由和爱，我的心真的很温暖。</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.new_bonds_of_unity.description>
    <!-- EN: vindicated skepticism -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.vindicated_skepticism.label>正确的怀疑</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.vindicated_skepticism.label>
    <!-- EN: It might be harsh, but our colony's stability and security come first. Their situation, while unfortunate, is a necessary stance to maintain order and prioritize our collective well-being. -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.vindicated_skepticism.description>这或许有些残酷，但我们殖民地的稳定和安全是第一位的。他们的处境虽然不幸，但却是维持秩序和优先考虑我们集体福祉的必要姿态。</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.vindicated_skepticism.description>
    <!-- EN: compassionate regret -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.compassionate_regret.label>同情的遗憾</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.compassionate_regret.label>
    <!-- EN: It's a real shame they couldn't officially join together here. Their love deserved a chance, and it's a pity we couldn't give it to them. -->
    <RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.compassionate_regret.description>真遗憾他们没能加入。他们的爱情应该有一个机会，可惜我们没能给他们机会。</RotR_BoFSpecMood.stages.compassionate_regret.description>
    
